        <h2>Branding</h2>
        <h3>Color</h3>
        <p>Based on my research, most environment-based companies chose green or blue as their brand color, so I knew I
            wanted to stray away from that. So I chose yellow because it’s a fun and cheerful color, and it also is a
            very hopeful color. For my secondary colors, I brought back the green palette to keep the
            environmentally-conscious message back into the brand.</p>
