        <h3>Typography</h3>
        <p>For the typeface of Second Life, I chose Poppins as the round corners emphasized the friendliness of the
            brand and it’s also an accessible and legible typeface. Most color and text color combinations meet WCAG AAA
            standards, with the stragglers meeting AA at an absolute minimum.</p>
